{"tid":763311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老泳池內突爆石　泳客聞異味驚逃 事後沒道歉霸氣離開","createTime":"2018-08-01T04:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T03:36:36.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60513df8eee9402e45f71846f8099844cd877df7","tid":763311,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:21:14.000Z","msg":"天氣炎熱，不少人會到泳池游泳消暑。惟江蘇蘇州一名老翁近日在游泳時，竟在泳池內大解，旁邊泳客見狀立即驚逃。泳池職員隨後把污物撈起，惟該名老翁沒有道歉便離開，惹來網上一遍罵聲。 <br />\n<br />\n從泳池閉路電視畫面可見，該名老翁一邊游泳，一邊「大解放」，期間他的動作未見異樣，惟池內傳出一陣難聞氣味，泳客紛紛上水避讓。游泳池負責人表示，夏天泳客太多，他們實難以管理；事後，泳池已即時換水，再投藥消毒保持水質乾淨，同時提供遊客退款補償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180801/mobile/bkn-20180801005310644-0801_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180801%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180801005310644-0801_00952_001.html&d=vdkkobhYCd2O8TjMKZdMc8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=eded4450\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180801/mobile/bkn-20180801005310644-0801_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c62a07b4a34b99756ae2f93d7c3e97b1a5a0e2","tid":763311,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的国"},{"pid":"458cc58bbedaa4e047e70cc135ab7448d94ecde8","tid":763311,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"哪兒來的屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc91587aa4b0a58f3f3c33aebec65634afc5eb4","tid":763311,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"真正解放軍"},{"pid":"f85bddd3ca82a8e56d6cf4153218612ac07e3094","tid":763311,"uid":196792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"{真}解放"},{"pid":"4f291fe752346b4191addb69cbdb58ddb6ace83c","tid":763311,"uid":74933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"